These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, card-games, singing, cooking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, cricket, water-polo, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is cricket##2
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
4. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person who's hobby is singing##6
5. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | cooking  | dancing | singing | card-games  |
| Sport   | weightlifting | water-polo   | basketball  | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, pineapple, kale, potato
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, musician, social-worker, fisherman
1. the fisherman is not to the left of the fisherman##8
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
3. the person eating artichoke is the musician##1
4. the person eating potato is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating pineapple##2
5. the person eating pineapple is somewhere between the person eating kale and the coach##7
6. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
7. the coach is not to the left of the coach##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | kale | pineapple          | potato | artichoke     |
| Job    | social-worker      | fisherman | coach | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dancer, police-officer, security-guard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, documentary, musical, horror
1. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the police-officer##8
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
3. the dancer is on the right of the coach##1
4. the dancer is in an even position##4
5. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
6. the coach is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
7. the security-guard is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | coach | dancer | police-officer     | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary    | horror   | spy | musical    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, pop, punk, reggae
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, handball, golf, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the fan of pop##1
4. the fan of reggae is not to the right of the person who's sport is golf##8
5. the fan of country is the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the fan of reggae##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | pop         | reggae   | country    |
| Sport         | handball | ice-hockey | golf | tennis |

