.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, horror, action, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting, volleyball, badminton
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching horror movies##7
2. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
3. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7
4. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
5. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person watching western movies##5
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | action | western | time-travel    |
| Sport         | water-polo | badminton   | volleyball   | weightlifting |

