.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapefruit, cabbage, apricot
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, reggae, jazz, r&b
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person eating carrot##5
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
5. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapefruit##5
6. the person eating apricot is not to the left of the fan of reggae##8
7. the person eating apricot is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | apricot | carrot | grapefruit  | cabbage |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | r&b         | jazz | gospel |

