.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, soy-milk, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, golf, sailing
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
2. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is golf##7
3. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
4. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | milk      | soy-milk | mirinda | juice   |
| Sport      | lacrosse | golf | sailing  | skateboarding |

