.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, paramedic, bartender, police-officer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, badminton, skateboarding, water-polo
1. the bartender is not to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
3. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the paramedic##7
5. the bartender is not to the right of the police-officer##8
6. the police-officer is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the bartender##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Job     | paramedic | bartender | police-officer | manager     |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | skateboarding        | water-polo          | badminton |

