.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, trance, funk, punk
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, roller, ship, snowmobile
1. the fan of rock is between the fan of punk and the person driving the van##2
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
4. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
5. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1
6. the fan of funk is not the person driving the ship##6
7. the fan of punk is not to the right of the fan of funk##8
8. the person driving the van is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | rock | funk | trance |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller       | van  | ship    |

