.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, artichoke, watermelon, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, dancing, drawing, writing
1. the person eating watermelon is not to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##8
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person eating artichoke##8
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating watermelon is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
6. the person eating artichoke is on the far left##1
7. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | artichoke        | strawberry | watermelon      | papaya    |
| Hobby   | video-games | drawing   | dancing | writing |

