.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, sprite, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, tennis, weightlifting, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##8
2. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person drinking mirinda##7
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
8. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda         | sprite    | iced-tea       |
| Sport      | tennis | badminton | swimming | weightlifting |

