.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, singing, traveling, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
2. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
4. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking mirinda and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade     | fanta | mirinda        | iced-tea       |
| Hobby      | traveling | singing  | rock-climbing | skydiving |

