.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, raspberry, orange, avocado
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, thriller, zombie, time-travel
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
 2. the person eating avocado is not to the left of the person eating orange##8
 3. the person eating strawberry is the person watching zombie movies##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 6. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
 7. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating strawberry is not to the right of the person watching zombie movies##8
 9. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the person eating strawberry##8
10. the person eating raspberry is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | raspberry    | orange | strawberry | avocado |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | time-travel  | zombie     | thriller    |

