.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, cauliflower, cranberry, apple
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, collecting, card-games, singing
1. the person eating cranberry is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person eating cranberry is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person eating apple##1
5. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
6. the person eating cauliflower is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person eating apple##2
7. the person eating cranberry is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | apple        | cauliflower | zucchini | cranberry |
| Hobby   | singing | card-games | collecting   | dancing    |

