.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, hamster, guinea-pig, pony
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, tram, ship, skateboard
1. the owner of the pony is not the person driving the ship##6
2. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the pony##7
4. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
5. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
6. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
7. the owner of the hamster is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | goat  | pony | hamster  | guinea-pig  |
| Transport   | taxi | tram   | skateboard | ship |

