.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, rabbit, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, tram, bus, ship
1. the person driving the tram is not the owner of the snake##6
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
4. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the boat##1
5. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the boat##7
6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the owner of the rabbit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig    | lizard | snake | rabbit |
| Transport   | tram | ship      | bus     | boat     |

 